name: CULTUR
description: $CULTUR is where memes, art, and storytelling collide. Led by the enigmatic ❤️Mr. E, we explore and preserve the cultures we love—games, TV shows, films, characters, and more. Our mission? To celebrate meme culture while delivering high-quality digital content and art that sets us apart. Join the movement and be part of a project that blends creativity, community, and culture like never before. The legend begins now. Are you ready?
